'''''Alhoria''''',  or '''''Al Horia''''', and possibly '''''Ajaraz Al Horia''''' is a newspaper based out of [[Khartoum]], [[Sudan]]. ''Huriya'' in Arabic translates to ''freedom'' in English. The newspaper was shut down for political reasons in April 2009.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://africanarguments.org/2009/04/21/elections-and-freedom-of-expression-in-sudan/|title=Sudan: Elections and Freedom of Expression - African Arguments|date=2009-04-21|work=African Arguments|access-date=2018-07-18|language=en-GB}}</ref>

