The '''Montenegrin Embassy in Ljubljana''' ([[Montenegrin language|Montenegrin]]: Ambasada Crne Gore u Ljubljani) is [[Montenegro]]'s diplomatic mission to the [[Slovenia]]. It is located at  Njegoševa cesta 14.

The current Ambassador of Montenegro to the Slovenia is [[Ranko Milović]]. 

